            </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>
        is the image of the orange part of the domain (the front triangle) the positive <m>z</m>-axis, the negative <m>z</m>-axis, the zero vector or the entire <m>z</m>-axis? 
            </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>
        is the image of the purple part of the domain (the back triangle) the positive <m>z</m>-axis, the negative <m>z</m>-axis, the zero vector or the entire <m>z</m>-axis?
